== Welcome to Beauty Salons Rails app

Rails is a web-application framework that includes everything needed to create
database-backed web applications according to the Model-View-Control pattern.

This app will show you all the salons with all their prices and services.

== Install 'Beauty Salons' App

1. Fetch git repository to you local machine:
       Repository: https://github.com/culis1989/beauty_salons

2. Navigate command line to a folder where you stored this repo and start rails server:
       rails s

3. Navigate command line to a folder where you stored this repo and run:
       1. rake db:migrate
       2. rake db:seed
